{"word":"ἀκόντισμα","slug":"ἀκόντισμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκόντισμα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀκοντίζω'><el>ἀκοντίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a javelin's throw</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>the thing thrown, a dart, javelin</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b>in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> = <el>ἀκοντισταί</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}